a45130cef6fad80502bd6ee2e3046e.poster.avif?t=1688245392\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/37a45130cef6fad80502bd6ee2e3046e.webm?t=1688245392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/37a45130cef6fad80502bd6ee2e3046e.mp4?t=1688245392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play the demo and if you like the game don't miss out on the <strong>special early access price</strong> as the game continues to grow and evolve!<br><br>With <strong>stylised graphics and arcade-like physics</strong>, every turn, straightway and ramp will put your skills to the test. <br><strong>Feel the thrill of the race like never before in VR</strong>, as you immerse yourself counting the seconds on the home stretch.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/e255545b0092835cd923a7a69d310d02.poster.avif?t=1688245392\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/e255545b0092835cd923a7a69d310d02.webm?t=1688245392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320470/extras/e255545b0092835cd923a7a69d310d02.mp4?t=1688245392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game features:<br>- Challenge unlock system: complete challenges to unlock cars, wheels, levels<br>- Game modes: race against your ghost and beat your best lap or race against AI opponents<br>- Garage: customize your car<br><br>Coming soon:<br>- UX improvements<br>- New level and challenges<br>- New cars and addons<br>- New game modes<br><br>So what are you waiting for? Get behind the wheel and start building your car today. <br><strong>The race is on!</strong>",
